Name: 2025 U.S. Open Golf Championship
Title: Third Round
Desc: Sam Burns carries the lead into the third round of the 125th U.S. Open from Oakmont Country Club.
LongDescription: Sam Burns carries the lead into the third round of the 125th U.S. Open from Oakmont Country Club. Burns shot a 5-under-par 65 to sit at -3, joined by 18-hole leader J.J. Spaun (-2) and Viktor Hovland (-1) as the only men below par after two days.
